 pepper, if desired. Cover to keep warm and set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Walnut sauce"},{"content":"Place walnuts into mixing bowl and dry roast <b>5 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>, <b>without measuring cup<b> or until fragrant and slightly darkened. Transfer into a small bowl and set aside."},{"content":"Place onion into mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 6<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula."},{"content":"Add oil and sauté <b>2 min\/120°C\/speed 2<b>."},{"content":"Add milk, vinegar, syrup, salt, pepper, reserved walnuts and 1 of the steamed garlic cloves and chop <b>10 sec\/speed 9<b>, then cook <b>4 min\/90°C\/speed 2<b> or until smooth and creamy. Transfer into a separate bowl."},{"content":"Arrange beetroot mixture onto a serving platter. Sprinkle with pine nuts (optional), garnish with extra curry leaves and serve with Walnut sauce."}],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h","4 portions"]}